data.description:
Country Setting - Sangamon Valley Schools, large yard, outskirts of Decatur. Rare find: ranch with a newer well (2021) and new septic (2023) Gutters (2023) HVAC (2023) Washer & Dryer (2023) Carpet (2023) Dishwasher (2023) Custom Tub Surround (2023) Relax on the concrete patio and have those cookouts.
Time to kick back and enjoy this location and one level home. Home Inspection Completed by Earth to Home 10-26-23.
Call your realtor this one will go quickly.
